Antonia Thomas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antonia_Thomas 0 Antonia Laura Thomas (born 3 November 1986) is an English actress. She is best known for starring as Alisha Daniels in the E4 comedy-drama series Misfits, Dr. Claire Browne in the ABC drama series The Good Doctor and Evie in the Channel 4/Netflix comedy series Lovesick.
